title: Surcode DVD Pro DTS Encoder v1.0.29.rar
description:
Overview
This version of SurCode? converts your 5.1 Surround Sound files to DTS format, for use in DVD Video or for making Surround Sound audio CDs.

SurCode can accept the 6 master soundfiles in either a .WAV or .AIFF format. SurCode outputs a ".dts" file, a ".dtp" file, or a ".wav" file.

If you are producing Video DVDs, you will use SurCode along with whatever DVD-authoring software you have. SurCode will output DTS-encoded soundfiles that you will then input into your DVD-authoring software.
